 * (e.g., \c ABT_pool_user_pop_fn()) later.  The implementation of this routine
 * may change its behavior based on the pool context \c context.
 *
 * @note
 * \DOC_DESC_POOL_CONTEXT_IMPL{\c context}
 *
 * \c ABT_pool_user_push_many_fn() is optional, so the user may set
 * \c ABT_pool_user_push_many_fn to \c NULL.
 *
